Package: workbch
Title: Lightweight Project Management
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Danielle",
           family = "Navarro",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "d.navarro@unsw.edu.au",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7648-6578"))
Description: A "work bench" to manage projects from within R. The 'workbch' 
    pcakge stores basic metadata (priority, deadlines, status) about projects, 
    allows filtering and search for projects, stores notes and tasks linked to
    projects, and assists navigation to web pages and folders linked to 
    projects.
